N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1806.35 - Fees

State Regulations

Project sponsors shall have an affirmative duty to pay such
fees as established by the commission to cover its costs of administering the
regulatory program established by this Part, including any extraordinary costs
associated with specific projects. Notes
